        "created_at": "2018-08-07T00:50:29.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Potinet-Ampeau release late, much like Robert Ampeau! That\u2019s why.</p>\n<p>Honestly, I think the best sense of what Rougeots can do is going to come from Coche. The others are just about unrealized potential.</p>\n<p>And the cabotte within the Clos is owned by two proprietors of the Clos des Rougeots, brothers or cousins I think. It is not in habitable condition, let\u2019s say.</p>",
